# Changelog

## [UNRELEASED]

- Fixed an issue with the `InputValidate.disable()` method that caused a runtime warning. Thanks to @mhanf for reporting and @cs42 for proposing a fix. (#10)

- `InputValidator.add_rule()` now composes validation rules rather than overwriting existing rules. (#14)

- All check functions in `shiny_validate.check` are now public, improving discoverability via autocomplete. (@mhanf #16)

## Version 0.1.1
- Relax shiny version requirement
- Bug fixes to check.required


## Version 0.1.0 
- Initital implementation
